</span><span class='line'>64 bytes from 1.1.1.1: <span class="nv">icmp_seq</span><span class="o">=</span>2 <span class="nv">ttl</span><span class="o">=</span>255 <span class="nb">time</span><span class="o">=</span>0.872 ms
